::Hevn::
       He shakes his head in disgust.  He roars after her, his voice booming. 
 "I BELIEVE YOU HAVE MISUNDERSTOOD ME!"  He fires two pairs of shots past her 
on either side.  "I no longer work for the Maximals.  I work for Nightlight, 
and until she tells me otherwise, that means protecting her as a Predacon.  
Are we clear now?  Now go, deliver my message and don't return, I doubt you 
would survive if you did."

--part1_4d.2fef70b6.2c042b04_boundary
